## Quick Reference

| Command | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `hx file.md` | Open file (auto-format on `:w`) |
| `hxf file.md` | Open file and format immediately |
| `:w` | Save (triggers auto-format) |
| `:fmt` | Manual format |
| `Space + t` | Custom table formatting |
